Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.63,TextCN,,0,0,0,,真的好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.31,TextCN,,0,0,0,,他在看什么书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.01,TextCN,,0,0,0,,喂喂 你看那个人好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.44,TextCN,,0,0,0,,超帅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.86,TextCN,,0,0,0,,去搭讪试试
