Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.40,TextCN,,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\pos(902,200)}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.46,TextCN,,0,0,0,,哎呀 小伙子真帅
